description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'Pilates for Better Sleep Workout' from the channel Lindywell, Pilates + Balanced Living by Robin Long.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Workout starts 00:40

Trying to improve the quality of your sleep? Give this new Pilates for Better Sleep routine a try!

This Pilates workout includes a balance of movement and stretching to help you reduce stress, relieve tension, wind down, and prepare for a good night of sleep. üòä
